title: Level1online's 32Gb RetroPie Image Updates and Fixes 08/23/2017
description: This is an updated version of my 32GB RetroPie backup. It has over 5,000 games ready to play. Please use SD Formatter to format your sd micro card. Then use Win32DiskImager to write the .img to your card. From there, eject the card and insert into your raspberry Pi 3. Dont forget to turn off the torrent before writing to avoid a permissions error. Please comment, like, and subscribe to my Youtube channel, I am the channel level1online Laters!
